OL,3,CKetamine could become a Class A drug,
OL,4,Cas government launch review
OL,6,FKetamine could be upgraded to a Class
OL,7,FA drug, as the government has
OL,8,Frequested a review of its
OL,9,Fclassification.
OL,11,FThe Home Office have written to the
OL,12,FAdvisory Council on the Misuse of
OL,13,FDrugs (ACMD) asking them to consider
OL,14,Fwhether it should remain as a Class B
OL,15,Fdrug or become a Class A.
OL,17,FThe move comes in response to record
OL,18,Fuse of the drug last year, with an
OL,19,Festimated 299,000 people aged 16-59
OL,20,Freporting having used ketamine in 2023.
