OL,6,FThe current Class B status means the
OL,7,Fmaximum penalty for supplying and
OL,8,Fproducing it is up to 14 years in
OL,9,Fprison, an unlimited fine, or both.
OL,11,FFor a Class A drug, the maximum
OL,12,Fpenalty for supply and production is
OL,13,Fup to life in prison, an unlimited
OL,14,Ffine, or both. For possession of a
OL,15,FClass A it's seven years in jail,
OL,16,Fcompared to five for a Class B.
