OL,6,FKetamine is one of the most detected
OL,7,Fdrugs in incidents of spiking, and is
OL,8,Falso often an ingredient so-called
OL,9,F'pink cocaine'. ITV News has reported
OL,10,Fon the rise in Brits using 'pink
OL,11,Fcocaine' abroad.
OL,13,FPolicing Minister Dame Diana Johnson
OL,14,Fsaid: "Ketamine is an extremely
OL,15,Fdangerous substance and the recent
OL,16,Frise in its use is deeply concerning.
