OL,6,F"Through our Plan for Change and
OL,7,Fmission to make the nation's streets
OL,8,Fsafer, we will work across health,
OL,9,Fpolicing and wider public services to
OL,10,Fdrive down drug use and stop those who
OL,11,Fprofit from its supply.
OL,13,F"It is vital we are responding to all
OL,14,Fthe latest evidence and advice to
OL,15,Fensure people's safety and we will
OL,16,Fcarefully consider the ACMD's
OL,17,Frecommendations before making any
OL,18,Fdecision."
