OL,3,CKetamine could become a Class A drug,
OL,4,Cas government launch review
OL,6,FThere have been a number of high
OL,7,Fprofile recent deaths caused by
OL,8,Fketamine consumption - including actor
OL,9,FMatthew Perry, who was found dead in
OL,10,Fhis hot tub in 2023 with a lethal
OL,11,Famount of ketamine in his blood stream.
OL,13,FIn November last year a coroner wrote
OL,14,Fto the Home Secretary calling for
OL,15,Furgent action over the classification
OL,16,Fof ketamine, after a man died due to
OL,17,F"long term-use" of the drug.
OL,19,FJames Boland, 38, from Manchester,
OL,20,Fdied of sepsis caused by a kidney
OL,21,Finfection as a result of ketamine use.
