OL,3,CKetamine could become a Class A drug,
OL,4,Cas government launch review
OL,6,FThe coroner said the Class B
OL,7,Fclassification for ketamine is "likely
OL,8,Fto encourage others to start to use it
OL,9,For continue to use it under the false
OL,10,Fimpression it is 'safer'."
OL,12,FIndependent experts on the ACMD will
OL,13,Fnow look at the evidence around the
OL,14,Fhealth and social harms of ketamine
OL,15,Fwhen used illegally, and will submit
OL,16,Ftheir findings to the Home Office to
OL,17,Freview.
